  02 Mar 2012; Andrew Savchenko <bircoph@gmail.com> orangefs-2.8.5.ebuild,
  files/pvfs2-server-conf.d, files/pvfs2-server-init.d,
  files/orangefs-2.8.5-layout.patch, files/orangefs-2.8.5-static-server.patch:
